{
  "page": "God-on-Earth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">The God-on-Earth</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Reign</th><td>\n10,000 years</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nGod-Emperor</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Predecessor</th><td>\nNone</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pearl_Emperor\" title=\"Pearl Emperor\">Pearl Emperor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pearl_Emperor\" title=\"Pearl Emperor\">Pearl Emperor</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nGod-on-Earth</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Great_Empire_of_the_Dawn\" title=\"Great Empire of the Dawn\">Great Empire of the Dawn</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Queen</th><td>\n100 queens</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pearl_Emperor\" title=\"Pearl Emperor\">Pearl Emperor</a><br />Son(s)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Lion_of_Night\" title=\"Lion of Night\">Lion of Night</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden-Made-of-Light\" title=\"Maiden-Made-of-Light\">Maiden-Made-of-Light</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>God-on-Earth</b> was the legendary first ruler of the mythic <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Empire_of_the_Dawn\" title=\"Great Empire of the Dawn\">Great Empire of the Dawn</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=God-on-Earth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to the tales told by the priestly scribes of <a href=\"/index.php/Yin\" title=\"Yin\">Yin</a>, he was the only begotten son of the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden-Made-of-Light\" title=\"Maiden-Made-of-Light\">Maiden-Made-of-Light</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Lion_of_Night\" title=\"Lion of Night\">Lion of Night</a>, and traveled about his domains in a <a href=\"/index.php/Palanquin\" title=\"Palanquin\">palanquin</a> carved from a single <a href=\"/index.php/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">pearl</a> and carried by a hundred queens, his wives. He ruled for ten thousand years, in which the empire flourished, until at last he ascended to the stars to join his forebears. He was succeeded by his eldest son, the <a href=\"/index.php/Pearl_Emperor\" title=\"Pearl Emperor\">Pearl Emperor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=God-on-Earth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" t